# voice-notify environment variables
#
# Default mode is local TTS — no keys required. This file is only needed
# if you want to upgrade to Fish Audio character voices or enable LLM
# summarization of Claude's last turn.

# === Optional: Fish Audio character voices ===
# Leave empty to use local TTS (macOS say / Linux espeak). No config needed.
# Get a key at: https://fish.audio
# FISH_API_KEY=

# === Optional: LLM summarization ===
# Without LLM, local mode speaks static text ("任务完成");
# with LLM, it summarizes what Claude just did.
# Required for Fish Audio API mode.
# Get a key at: https://platform.deepseek.com
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=

# === Optional: Use OpenAI-compatible API instead of DeepSeek ===
# LLM_API_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions
# LLM_API_KEY=your_key
# LLM_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
